abstract: Bobbi Kristina Brown, 21-year-old daughter of late singer Whitney Houston, is taken to the hospital after she is found unresponsive in a bathtub at her Atlanta home.
lead_paragraph: Bobbi Kristina Brown, the daughter of Whitney Houston and Bobby Brown, was taken to a hospital and was alive on Saturday, a police spokeswoman said.

headline.main: Whitney Houston’s Daughter Found Unresponsive in Tub
headline.print_headline: Whitney Houston’s Daughter Found Limp in Tub
